      "writtenOn": "2017-11-17T16:38:04Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "it seems that you will either have to dup this code for every config entity, or generalize using reflection. I recommend the latter.\nhttps://godoc.org/github.com/golang/protobuf/proto#GetProperties can be used to retrieve properties and compose queries. This can be done in a separate CL when we verify that this works",
      "revId": "4ac64e9835cdc5fa6b35137797a21dd99ad2254e",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
